text: Ella Hunt (born 29 April 1998) is an English actress and singer. She was nominated for a Scottish BAFTA for her role in the movie Anna and the Apocalypse (2017). She also had roles in television, such as in Cold Feet (2016–2017) and Dickinson (2019–2021).
